<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-67-1130 </DOCNO><TEXT>A description of the CUSB-II bismuth germanate calorimeter is presented.Details of the design philosophy are given, together with the performancecharacteristics. Energy resolution results obtained with 5 GeV Bhabhascattering events and with radiative photons from electric dipole transitionsfrom the third excited upsilon state to the second excited P state arepresented.</TEXT></DOC>